Subject: [SCSA-015] Remote Denial of Service Vulnerability in PowerFTP




======================================================================
Security Corporation Security Advisory [SCSA-015]

Remote Denial of Service Vulnerability in PowerFTP
======================================================================

PROGRAM: PowerFTP
HOMEPAGE: http://www.cooolsoft.com
VULNERABLE VERSIONS: 2.25 and prior ?
RISK: Medium/High
IMPACT: Denial Of Service
RELEASE DATE: 2003-04-01

======================================================================
